description:
Operation Boomerang

This is perhaps the most unusual story ever presented in this day and age... fiction? Maybe! ...truth? ....only time will tell!

The Making Of A Man

Gerard Miller was smaller and not as tough as the other kids around the Indiana town where he grew up! He always backed away from a fight... never dove off the high diving board, was afraid of hunting because he hated guns, shunned football because Mrs. Miller didn't want her only son to get hurt! This was the material the Army got when they drafted Gerard Miller in March, 1960! A weakling, a coward, and a mama's boy!

Chip Off the Old Block (Text Only Story)

2 Against 10,000

The pilot though ground-pounders were rejects who couldn't make the Air Force! In addition, he thought they had a nice, safe racket compared with flying a jet up in Mig Alley -- and he didn't mind telling Turk Arajanian that when the Army Sergeant voiced his own opinion of fly-boys who couldn't load a browning automatic rifle or field-strip an M1! In a word, they hated each other... but they shared a greater hate... of the enemy!
name: Operation Boomerang; The Making Of A Man; Chip Off the Old Block; 2 Against 10,000
A Privates War; Power Play; Reunion On Hill 119; Yella!

description: Tinker Bell and friends embark upon on a magical quest to face down a dragon! In Never Land, the Fairy Bess needs to find a magic powder that is vital to sustain the talents of the Fairies of Pixie Hollow. The only place to find this special substance is in a mountain where the fearsome dragon Kyto dwells. It's up to Tinker Bell, Terence and Prilla to save the day!
name: Tinker Bell and The Day of the Dragon

description:
A Collection of Volumes 7 - 9!

I love you like a brother.

He loves me like a lover.

Shinogu's deepest secret is exposed...the one that will take him out of Hatsumi's life forever. If you think being a teenager is hard, wait until you read Hot Gimmick--these Tokyo boys and girls are really messed up!

After Ryoki has a New Year's mishap, Hatsumi's older brother, Shinogu's darkest secret has been exposed... And it could take him out of Hatsumi's life for good!
name: Vol. 3

description:
A Collection of Volumes 10 - 12!

Final Volume!

Heads or tails?

If only love were that easy

When Hatsumi learns the truth about Azusa's mother, it spoils her relationship with Ryoki But enough to make her run into the arms of Shinogu?!

On the final omnibus volume, Hatsumi learns the truth about Azua's mother, and it results in a strain on her relationship with Ryoki. However, it's enough for her to run back into the arms of Shinogu...
name: Vol. 4
